- As a video gamer, I want to be able to build a team with the same nationality
- As a player rater, I want to know the top players for each skill set
- As an EA developer, I want to understand the variation of players skill stats
- As a video gamer, I want to be able to specify the configuration of a team of players
- As a video gamer, I want to build the best team based on any formation
- As a video gamer, I want to be able to compare players
- As an EA developer, I want to visual graph of players skills distribution
- As as a video gamer, I want to see the relationships between different skill sets
